metadata.description:
i told god that i wanna be free flowin
no more stagnant water n*gga 
welcome to my ocean

todo // siempre // todo // cambia


written, performed, and produced by tulengua
mixed by andre elias
mastered by robert st. thomas

lyrics.text:
[Intro: Alan Lili, Amari Jordan , Jamia]
Todo siempre, todo cambia

Low light (light)
Dark night (night)
Come alive baby
Come alive (lay back)
Unwind (unwind)
Red wine (red wine)
Come alive baby
Come alive (like this)

[Pre verse: Alan Lili, Amari Jordan]
Maybe we’ve been caught in limbo (todo siempre, todo cambia)
Maybe we can take it slow (todo siempre, todo cambia)
Drifting out that open window (todo siempre, todo cambia)
I guess that’s just the way it goes
(It's the way it goes, todo siempre, todo cambia)

[Verse 1: Amari Jordan]
I told God that i wanna be be free flowing
No more stagnant water, nigga welcome to my ocean
Required higher conscious, yea it took all of my focus
I was broken, now i’m coaching and i need new diagnosis
Took a breath when i had this epiphany
God called she sound like a symphony
In the present, forgot all my history
Broke chains pull up on my victory
How it take this long to notice me?
I was spitting that crack, shroom potency
Collision, tongue on smooth poetry
That’s that rap, hang facts of diplomacy
Graduated
And i’m just happy that you made it
How are you lately?
Open up, come alive, i’m patient
Oh yea i’m saying
I've been waiting so long

[Chorus 1: tulengua, Alan Lili, Amari Jordan, Jamia]
Swear we’ve had it all from the start (todo siempre, todo cambia)
Maybe i’m just playing my part
(Spread your wings to the sky, super fly, never die)
Lately i’ve been falling apart (todo siempre, todo cambia)
Holy power burns in my heart (Fire)

[Verse 2: Alan Lili, Amari Jordan]
Le dije a dios que me construya un corazón de astronauta
Dejo atrás lo que conozco y al pasado pura espalda
Me uno con el cielo, a vivir de aventurero
Mamá no llores si me muero, todo regresa en algo nuevo
Si he caido diez, once seguí
En babylon corriendo, maratón pa' aquí
Esta es mi tierra, mi vida llena
Cuando acabe, yo los quiero ver
Bailando cumbia en el entierro
Celebración puro perreo
Como un buen cuento, nunca muero
Siempre estoy vivo en los que quiero

Quiero
Quiero (como un buen)
Quiero (come alive)
Que quiero
Yeah
Quiero (low light)
Quiero
Ita, no lloren si muero
Siempre estoy vivo en los que quiero

[Chorus 2: tulengua, Alan Lili, Amari Jordan]
Swear we’ve had it all from the start (todo siempre, todo cambia)
Maybe I’m just playing my part
(come alive yeah yeah, come alive)
Lately I’ve been falling apart (holy power)
Holy power burns in my heart (it's real)

[Bridge: Alan Lili, Jamia]
Scared to take the fall from a hill so tall
And I could have it all if want to
Scared to take the fall yeah
I could drop the ball yeah
We could have it all if we want to

(Wings to the sky, super fly, never die)

[Outro Hook: Alan Lili, Jamia]
Todo siempre, todo cambia
Low light (light)
Dark night (night)
Come alive baby
Come alive (maybe we can take it slow)
Unwind (unwind)
Red wine (red wine)
Come alive baby
Come alive (i guess that's just the way it goes)

[Chorus 3: Alan Lili & Amari Jordan & Jamia, Amari Jordan, Jamia]
Swear we’ve had it all from the start (todo siempre, todo cambia)
Maybe I’m just playing my part
(Spread your wings to the sky, super fly, never die)
Lately I’ve been falling apart (it's real power)
Holy power burns in my heart (todo siempre, todo cambia)
